@inherits BlogPost
@{
    Page.Title = "First Post";
    //For BlogPost, a Published date is required
    //Use the short form with a string or the full DateTime constructor.
    Page.Published = "2025-07-01";
    Page.Published = new DateTime(2025, 7, 1);

    //Tags: Comma separated
    Page.Tags = "first";
}

<Markdown>

    ## Making a Blog post

    By inheriting the type @(nameof(BlogPost)) the razor page will be included in the list of **posts and the feeds**.

    This post was written in markdown by wrapping it in `&lt;Markdown&gt;&lt;/Markdown&gt;`

